        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Anthony Fothergill was an English physician. In 1803 he retired from practice and moved to Philadelphia and then returned to England with the prospect of war in 1812.</p>
        </bioghist>
